---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-surface-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 sm:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-xs">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <div class="flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[var(--color-primary-600)] text-xs font-bold text-white">
            A
          </div>
          <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
            Agents 特区
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          一线实践者的AI agent管理经验，从个人探索到组织级实践。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-8 text-sm">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="/articles" class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text-primary)] transition-colors">文章</a>
          <a href="/authors" class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text-primary)] transition-colors">作者</a>
          <a href="/tags" class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text-primary)] transition-colors">话题</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text-primary)] transition-colors">RSS</a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/lipingtababa/agentszone-ai"
            class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text-primary)] transition-colors"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            投稿 <span class="inline-block translate-y-[-1px] text-[10px] opacity-50">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-[var(--color-surface-border)] pt-6">
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        &copy; {year} Agents 特区
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
